featureType.title: dse_vmtrans_tr_road_2
featureType.abstract: This is a duplication of the original object dse_vmtrans_tr_road. The ideal situation is to have this layer with two styles: one for the use in VicMapClassic layer group and the other to use it for the dynamic labels layer but GeoServer does not allow it. In the layer group we can only use the default style. Even though GeoServer is prepared to change the style dynamically, it does not work. So the workaround was to duplicate the object and create two styles, one for each purpose.
